title: La Cuisine
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Health food restaurant and shop. Offering daily changing items with salads, sandwiches, wraps, smoothies, juices, and more. Vegan special is written on a chalk board. Vegan dinner might include soup, vegetable curry, pasta pomodoro with vegan cheese, or almond falafel. Healthy and raw desserts available. Store sells energy bars, hemp powder, chia seeds, granola, rice cakes, teas, and other products.
streetAddress: Calle 11 entre 5 y 10 Sur Col. Gonzalo Guerrero
